Summary: One bag was nuff fur me pardner
Text: How "D" ma fren. I'z setten here figurin what to do with the other 3 bags I gots with this odor. Already gave the kids nex-door Dia-Beet-is. Jus kidden a course. 8 all that came ta me and luved every bite. Good lil suckers...try them urself. I knows u'll be back fur more. Yahoo pardner.
